## ğŸ”¹ Comparison Table

| Modifier    | Same Class | Child Class | Outside Class |
| ----------- | ---------- | ----------- | ------------- |
| `local`     | âœ… Yes      | âŒ No        | âŒ No          |
| `protected` | âœ… Yes      | âœ… Yes       | âŒ No          |
| *(default)* | âœ… Yes      | âœ… Yes       | âœ… Yes         |

---

## ğŸ”¹ Default (No Modifier)

If you don't specify anything:

```systemverilog
