  function void run();
    calc();   // âœ… allowed
  endfunction
endclass

packet p = new();
// p.calc();  âŒ NOT allowed
```

### âœ… Explanation:

* Parent class â†’ allowed
* Child class â†’ allowed
* Outside â†’ âŒ not allowed

---

## ğŸ”¹ Important Rule âš ï¸

### âŒ You CANNOT override a `local` method

```systemverilog
